WordPress,com,is,the,hosted,version,of,the,popular,open,source,blogging,software,WordPress,com,exposes,site,post,comment,and,like,data,via,an,REST,Application,Programming,Interface,API,in,a,JSON,format,The,OAuth,protocol,is,used,for,authentication,The,standard,WordPress,XML,RPC,API,is,also,supported,by,WordPress,com,using,OAuth,and,basic,auth